result.markdown: --- title: "Week 7: ARIMA models" --- ::: {.cell} ::: ## Tutorial exercises - Complete Exercises 5, 7, 11, 14 from [Section 8.8 of the book](https://otexts.com/fpp3/expsmooth-exercises.html). - [Tutorial learning objectives](tute-lo.qmd). ## What you will learn this week * Stationarity and differencing * Random Walk Models ## Pre-seminar activities Read [Sections 9.1-9.2 of the textbook](https://otexts.com/fpp3/arima.html) and watch all embedded videos. ## Assignments * [GA2](../assignments/G2.qmd) is due on Monday 14 April. * [IA3](../assignments/A3.qmd) is due on Monday 28 April. * [GA3](../assignments/G3.qmd) is due on Monday 05 May.
